<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Tabs - SURF Example</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --glass-bg: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.4);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --accent-primary: #38bdf8;
            --accent-secondary: #818cf8;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-dim: #94a3b8;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #1e1b4b, #0f172a);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: var(--text-main);
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 650px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, var(--accent-primary) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -0.04em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .tabs-container {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 32px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .tab-buttons {
            display: flex;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 0.5rem;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .tab-btn {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.23, 1, 0.32, 1);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            border-radius: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tab-btn:hover {
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .tab-btn[data-active="true"] {
            color: var(--text-main);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .tab-btn[data-active="true"]::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 6px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 20px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--accent-primary);
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--accent-primary);
        }

        .tab-content {
            padding: 3rem;
            text-align: left;
            min-height: 250px;
        }

        .tab-panel {
            animation: slideIn 0.4s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(10px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        .tab-panel h3 {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        }

        .tab-panel p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .back {
            position: fixed;
            top: 2rem;
            left: 2rem;
            color: var(--text-dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .back:hover {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            transform: translateX(-5px);
        }

        code {
            display: block;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 24px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <a href="/showcase/06-layout" class="back" d-pulse="navigate">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"
            stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <line x1="19" y1="12" x2="5" y2="12"></line>
            <polyline points="12 19 5 12 12 5"></polyline>
        </svg>
        Back
    </a>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tabbed Interface</h1>

        <div class="tabs-container" d-cell="{ tab: 1 }" d-id="tabs-demo">
            <div class="tab-buttons">
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 1" d-attr="data-active:tab == 1">
                    Vision
                </button>
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 2" d-attr="data-active:tab == 2">
                    Core
                </button>
                <button class="tab-btn" d-signal="click: tab = 3" d-attr="data-active:tab == 3">
                    Open
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="tab-content">
                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 1">
                    <h3>The Vision</h3>
                    <p>SURF is a revolutionary HTML-first framework that restores control to the server. By treating the
                        DOM as a series of reactive surfaces, we eliminate the complexity of heavy client-side state
                        management.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 2" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>Core Engine</h3>
                    <p>Powered by reactive Surfaces and isolated Cells. Features include declarative signals, automatic
                        server synchronization, and state survival protocols that ensure a seamless user journey.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tab-panel" d-show="tab == 3" style="display: none;">
                    <h3>Open Access</h3>
                    <p>Built for the developer community. SURF is open source, free forever, and designed without vendor
                        lock-in. Experience the freedom of building high-performance web applications with zero
                        friction.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <code>
&lt;div d-cell="{ tab: 1 }"&gt;
  &lt;button d-signal="tab = 1" d-attr="data-active: tab == 1"&gt;Vision&lt;/button&gt;
  &lt;div d-show="tab == 1"&gt;Content goes here...&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
        </code>
    </div>

    <%- include('../../partials/core-scripts') %>
</body>

</html>